1. *Iznenađena* sam tvojim dolaskom. (I am surprised by your arrival.)
2. Nisam bila *iznenađena* njegovim odgovorom. (I wasn't surprised by his response.)
3. Ona je ostala *iznenađena* kada je čula tu vest. (She was shocked when she heard the news.)
4. Kada su mi rekli da sam dobio posao, bio sam veoma *iznenađen*. (When they told me I got the job, I was very surprised.)
5. Bila je *iznenađena* koliko se topla može biti voda u bazenu. (She was surprised at how warm the water in the pool can be.)
6. Iako je očekivao loše vesti, bio je *iznenađen* kada mu je doktor rekao dijagnozu. (Although he expected bad news, he was surprised when the doctor told him the diagnosis.)
7. Ona je bila *iznenađena* da je njen pas naučio da otvara vrata. (She was surprised that her dog learned how to open doors.)
8. *Iznenađujuća* vest se pojavila u novinama. (A surprising news appeared in the newspapers.)
9. Njegov *iznenađujući* odgovor nas je sve ostavio bez reči. (His surprising response left us all speechless.)
10. Kada sam videla da mi je sestra došla u posetu, bila sam *iznenađeno* srećna. (When I saw my sister came to visit me, I was pleasantly surprised.)